Due to the correlation of genotypes between discordant sibs, the covariance between the two log odds ratios needs to be considered. Based on the multivariate hypergeometric distribution assumption, we can calculate the variance and covariance for the two odds ratios. The detailed derivation is shown in Additional file 1. Based on the derivation, the covariance is calculated as follows4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
